<h2>Common iPhone Issues We Fix</h2>
<h3>Cracked Screens</h3>
<p>One of the most prevalent issues faced by iPhone users is a cracked screen. Accidental drops or bumps can lead to unsightly cracks that not only affect the aesthetics but also the functionality of your device.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Fast Repairs:</strong> Most cracked screen replacements can be completed in under 30 minutes.</li>
  <li><strong>Quality Assurance:</strong> We use OEM-standard parts to ensure durability and longevity.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Battery Problems</h3>
<p>Is your iPhone battery draining faster than usual? Over time, batteries lose their ability to hold a charge, leading to frustration during daily use.</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>Signs of Battery Issues:</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Rapid battery drain</li>
      <li>Swelling or bulging</li>
      <li>Overheating during charging</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
<p>At iFixScreens, we offer quick battery replacement services that can restore your device's performance.</p>
<h3>Water Damage</h3>
<p>Accidental spills or drops in water can lead to significant damage. If your iPhone has been exposed to liquid, it's essential to seek professional help immediately.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Expert Repair:</strong> Our technicians are trained to handle water-damaged devices and can often restore functionality.</li>
  <li><strong>Preventive Measures:</strong> Quick action can prevent further damage and increase the chances of successful repair.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Camera Malfunctions</h3>
<p>A malfunctioning camera can hinder your ability to capture moments. Whether it's a cracked lens or software issues affecting functionality, we've got you covered.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Quick Turnaround:</strong> Camera repairs can often be completed within 30 minutes.</li>
  <li><strong>Affordable Solutions:</strong> We provide competitive pricing for all camera-related repairs.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Sound Issues</h3>
<p>If you're experiencing problems with sound during calls or media playback, it could be due to speaker or microphone issues.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Diagnosis and Repair:</strong> Our technicians will diagnose the problem and provide effective solutions to restore sound quality.</li>
</ul>

